/u></h2><p class="font-medium text-base lg:text-lg mb-5 last-of-type:mb-0 [&amp;&gt;u]:no-underline [&amp;&gt;u]:text-tm-c-primary">Introducing our first purpose-built product for the indoor game. Designed with one goal in mind: to create the ultimate indoor golf experience.</p><div class="flex gap-5 mt-6 flex-col md:flex-row items-center"><a target="_self" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap text-base xl:text-lg font-medium tracking-tight ring-offset-white transition-colors focus-visible:outline-hidden disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 dark:ring-offset-neutral-950 text-tm-c-light border-2 rounded-md border-tm-c-primary w-full max-w-[320px] text-center bg-tm-c-primary hover:bg-[#ab490e] hover:border-[#ab490e] h-10 px-4 py-2" href="/golf/launch-monitors/trackman-io">Discover more</a></div></div></div></section><section class="px-10 lg:px-0 bg-tm-c-dark text-tm-c-light pt-[5rem] pb-[5rem]"><div class="grid-container"><div class="relative self-center aspect-square col-start-1 col-span-4 md:mr-5 lg:mr-0 lg:col-start-3 lg:col-span-6 xl:col-start-7 xl:col-span-9 row-start-1 mb-6 md:mb-0"><img alt="Two TrackMan devices, one orange and one gray, featuring sleek designs with visible branding and metallic accents, used for sports analytics." loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="w-full h-full object-cover" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="100vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fa.storyblok.com%2Ff%2F117513%2F900x900%2Feafa3f75f4%2Flaunch_monitor_tm_4_trackman_golf_webp.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=100 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fa.storyblok.com%2Ff%2F117513%2F900x900%2Feafa3f75f4%2Flaunch_monitor_tm_4_trackman_golf_webp.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=100 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fa.storyblok.com%2Ff%2F117513%2F900x900%2Feafa3f75f4%2Flaunch_monitor_tm_4_trackman_golf_webp.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=100 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fa.sto