ors, and innovative sports tracking technology. Elevate your game. Explore now!\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"4\",{\"rel\":\"canonical\",\"href\":\"https://www.trackman.com/apple-touch-icon.png\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"5\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"x-default\",\"href\":\"https://www.trackman.com\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"6\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"en\",\"href\":\"https://www.trackman.com\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"7\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"fr\",\"href\":\"https://www.trackman.com/fr\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"8\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"es\",\"href\":\"https://www.trackman.com/es\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"9\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"it\",\"href\":\"https://www.trackman.com/it\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"10\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"ko\",\"href\":\"https://www.trackman.com/ko\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"11\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"ja\",\"href\":\"https://www.trackman.com/ja\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"12\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"de\",\"href\":\"https://www.trackman.com/de\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"13\",{\"property\":\"og:title\",\"content\":\"Trackman: Golf Simulators, Launch Monitors \u0026 Sports Tech\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"14\",{\"property\":\"og:description\",\"content\":\"Discover Trackman's leading golf simulators, advanced launch monitors, and innovative sports tracking technology. Elevate your game. Explore now!\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"15\",{\"property\":\"og:url\",\"content\":\"https://www.trackman.com/apple-touch-icon.png\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"16\",{\"property\":\"og:image\",\"content\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/1200x630/5249298996/og_trackman.jpg\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"17\",{\"property\":\"og:type\",\"content\":\"website\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"18\",{\"name\":\"twitter:card\",\"content\":\"summary_large_image\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"19\",{\"name\":\"twitter:site\",\"content\":\"@trackmangolf\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"20\",{\"name\":\"twitter:title\",\"content\":\"Trackman: Golf Simulators, Launch Monitors \u0026 Sports Tech\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"21\",{\"name\":\"twitter:description\",\"content\":\"Discover Trackman's leading golf simulators, advanced launch monitors, and innovative sports tracking technology. Elevate your game. Explore now!\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"22\",{\"name\":\"twitter:image\",\"content\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/1200x630/5249298996/og_trackman.jpg\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"23\",{\"rel\":\"icon\",\"href\":\"/apple-touch-icon.png/icon.png?b70ae80b1ea368e4\",\"type\":\"image/png\",\"sizes\":\"454x454\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"24\",{\"name\":\"next-size-adjust\"}]]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"9:null\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"ba:I[64887,[\"2805\",\"static/chunks/2805-7cbf0c47eb9884ac.js\",\"3019\",\"static/chunks/3019-bd094b4e0808d762.js\",\"6495\",\"static/chunks/app/%5Blang%5D/page-663ed711240584b0.js\"],\"default\"]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"19:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-tm-c-dark text-tm-c-light py-20 px-5 lg:px-0\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"grid-container\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"col-start-1 col-span-4 md:col-start-2 md:col-span-6 lg:col-start-3 lg:col-span-12 min-[1165px]:col-start-2 min-[1165px]:col-[span_14_/_span_14] xl:col-start-4 xl:col-[span_26_/_span_26] 3xl:col-start-7 3xl:col-[span_20_/_span_20]\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex w-full justify-center text-center mb-6\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"lg:max-w-[700px] [\u0026_span]:text-tm-c-light!\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"mb-6 [\u0026\u003eu]:no-underline [\u0026\u003eu]:text-tm-c-primary\",\"children\":[\"Discover more\",[\"$\",\"br\",\"0\",{}]]}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex flex-col xl:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-5\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L14\",\"152019747152116\",{\"href\":\"/blog/golf/how-trackman-360-transforms-the-golf-club-for-players\",\"className\":\"w-full min-w-[320px] xl:max-w-[340px]\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$b1\",null,{\"fallback\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-full h-[130px] md:h-[480px] overflow-hidden grid border-none shadow-lg\"}],\"children\":[\"$\",\"$Lb2\",null,{\"reason\":\"next/dynamic\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$Lba\",null,{\"cardData\":{\"name\":\"How Trackman 360 transforms the golf club for players\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T13:29:56.074Z\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-13T08:23:12.422Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-13T08:23:12.440Z\",\"id\":152019747152116,\"uuid\":\"7c81b85b-4314-40d2-ab6f-c7108ab29c8f\",\"content\":{\"seo\":{\"_uid\":\"a17e7e79-ed0d-49ba-9eff-b6a7516faf2d\",\"title\":\"How Trackman 360 transforms the golf club experience for players\",\"plugin\":\"seo_metatags\",\"og_image\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/2400x1260/62674545c0/og_trackman_360_players_blog.webp\",\"og_title\":\"How Trackman 360 transforms the golf club experience for players\",\"description\":\"Trackman 360 connects range, simulators and data so members can practice with purpose, track progress and enjoy an engaging club experience year-round.\",\"twitter_image\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/2400x1260/62674545c0/og_trackman_360_players_blog.webp\",\"twitter_title\":\"How Trackman 360 transforms the golf club experience for players\",\"og_description\":\"Trackman 360 connects range, simulators and data so members can practice with purpose, track progress and enjoy an engaging club experience year-round.\",\"twitter_description\":\"Trackman 360 connects range, simulators and data so members can practice with purpose, track progress and enjoy an engaging club experience year-round.\"},\"_uid\":\"cc19c70d-0bf1-48c5-be78-31e5c8b1219a\",\"body\":[{\"_uid\":\"b301d3d9-c748-4543-a7af-28b61ca52d20\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The golf club of today doesn’t just revolve around tee times anymore. For golfers, the modern club experience starts at arrival and extends across the range, simulator, coaching sessions, and course — creating one connected journey from first swing to final putt.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Trackman 360\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/lp/trackman-360\",\"uuid\":\"79bd296d-af16-4bd4-a9b2-6adf472b3da3\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]},{\"text\":\" is designed to do exactly that, linking range, indoor golf simulators, coaching insights, and player profiles into a single unified ecosystem.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"While operators see \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"improved utilization and revenue\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/blog/golf/trackman-360-for-golf-businesses\",\"uuid\":\"d78ee8e6-4e33-4c54-a89e-d45433da79cd\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]},{\"text\":\", and \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"coaches fill more lesson slots\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/blog/golf/why-coaches-are-building-their-programs-on-trackman-360\",\"uuid\":\"f2112f59-7baa-460c-bef2-79120c48ce87\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]},{\"text\":\", the golfer experiences something else: clarity, engagement, and measurable improvement.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"At Royal Drottningholm Golf Club, Black Desert Resort, and Eaglewood Golf Course, golfers describe a shift that goes far beyond the technology.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"b25db6fc-4497-4ccf-96b1-ded507c786be\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"e0a54745-0632-4ccc-97a9-0e87545d8a87\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Golf technology that’s easy to use\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Great technology should disappear into the experience. Trackman’s value isn’t just what it measures — it’s how quickly golfers can begin using it, without friction, confusion, or time spent figuring things out. When practice starts with a few taps instead of a complicated setup, golfers are more likely to show up, hit more balls, and come back again.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"At \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"Black Desert\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/success-stories/black-desert-resort\",\"uuid\":\"94bf1cad-f584-4699-95f7-711ea9bc4e3c\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]},{\"text\":\" in the US, Mike du Tois highlights how easy it is for members like himself to start a session — even if only for a quick warm-up.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"“\",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"When I walk up and I’m looking to hit a couple balls before a round, it’s just a matter of pressing a couple buttons on the touchscreen and I’m off and running,\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\"}]},{\"text\":\"” says Mike. \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"“I truly love the Trackman user interface. It’s the simplest, the easiest to use, and it has the best graphics out there.”\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"And when it’s a more serious session, the technology still stays out of the way — while keeping every number connected to his profile.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"“I can just scan the QR code, connect my account, and then I’ll have that data available so I can go back and do some analysis,”\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\"}]},{\"text\":\" says Mike.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Read the full story of Black Desert Resort\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/success-stories/black-desert-resort\",\"uuid\":\"94bf1cad-f584-4699-95f7-711ea9bc4e3c\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"c31339be-175f-49d5-be1b-5becb2c4fd40\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"5b15b414-98dc-492b-9c17-5196ec5939c7\",\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"post_video\",\"video_url\":\"https://vimeo.com/1164606658/3b5a1ef1de?share=copy\u0026fl=sv\u0026fe=ci\",\"play_icon_theme\":\"white\",\"video_thumbnail\":{\"id\":152022854791609,\"alt\":\"A man wearing a cap and vest is seated, speaking in a dimly lit room. Text on screen says, \\\"Mike Du Tois, Customer.\\\"\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"360_players_mike_thumbnail\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/3840x2160/80f9101375/360_players_mike_thumbnail.jpg\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"A man wearing a cap and vest is seated, speaking in a dimly lit room. Text on screen says, \\\"Mike Du Tois, Customer.\\\"\",\"title\":\"360_players_mike_thumbnail\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false}},{\"_uid\":\"5ef37e0e-1427-423b-9d2d-9270867162d6\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Practice with purpose: From guesswork to game plan\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"But ease of use is only the beginning. The biggest difference players feel isn’t that Trackman provides more numbers — it’s that the numbers make practice instantly more purposeful. Ball flight, yardages, spin rates, and performance metrics turn a warm-up into a plan, and a plan into real preparation that carries onto the course.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"When the same feedback follows you indoors and outdoors, improvement stops being seasonal or accidental and starts becoming intentional. At Black Desert, Mike describes how having accurate yardages available before a round can change the entire day of golf.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"“It’s just more accessible being able to come to the simulators or go to the range and have all those numbers readily available. There weren’t many opportunities to have a launch monitor or to play on simulators in the past, so I’m really loving this,”\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\"}]},{\"text\":\" says Mike.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"m\",\"_uid\":\"8f71cd63-a2bf-48c0-bc8c-79fe0c23d411\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"116c3599-9c58-4fb0-8c38-1a551bec4076\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Measurable improvement and confidence gains\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"connected Trackman 360 practice experience\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/blog/golf/trackman-360-powering-clubs-empowering-players\",\"uuid\":\"c4c6a52c-f911-46d8-83fe-9d47c6d700ae\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]},{\"text\":\" doesn’t just improve performance — it changes how golfers feel about their game. When players can measure progress and understand what happened on a good shot (or a bad one), confidence becomes more stable and practice becomes more rewarding. That confidence is often what keeps golfers engaged long-term.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"At \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"Eaglewood \",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/success-stories/eaglewood-golf-course\",\"uuid\":\"7f897fca-b429-4b7a-8e90-f10c2ed59d84\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]},{\"text\":\"in the US, member Court Huish links that enjoyment directly to the data — and to how much more he practices because of it.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"“Trackman just makes it so much more enjoyable because of all the information it provides on carry, distance, and all the angles. It’s a remarkable system. I’ve probably doubled or tripled my use of the driving range,”\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\"}]},{\"text\":\" says Court.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Read the full story of Eaglewood Golf Course\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/success-stories/eaglewood-golf-course\",\"uuid\":\"7f897fca-b429-4b7a-8e90-f10c2ed59d84\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"3783f673-82a4-4148-848a-00b28bf4ee5b\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"d1a7bd2b-1660-476e-a7a4-c71afe1b902e\",\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"post_video\",\"video_url\":\"https://vimeo.com/1132111386/f49fb70342?share=copy\u0026fl=sv\u0026fe=ci\",\"play_icon_theme\":\"white\",\"video_thumbnail\":{\"id\":152025925662089,\"alt\":\"Elderly man in a red shirt and white cap sitting in a golf driving range, smiling, with golf bags and a TV screen in the background.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"360_players_court_thumbnail\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/3840x2160/4b38c5d387/360_players_court_thumbnail.jpg\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Elderly man in a red shirt and white cap sitting in a golf driving range, smiling, with golf bags and a TV screen in the background.\",\"title\":\"360_players_court_thumbnail\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false}},{\"_uid\":\"05653093-0e90-49b8-8805-a9e1b4ab835a\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Year-round golf: No off-season anymore\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Trackman 360 doesn’t just make practice better — it makes it more consistent. When indoor and outdoor environments are connected, clubs can maintain momentum through winter, heat, and limited daylight. Players don’t have to “restart” their progress each season, and clubs don’t have to accept long stretches of quiet.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"At Eaglewood, which endures harsh Rocky Mountain winters, Trackman 360 has extended operating hours and reshaped what’s possible for working golfers — making the facility usable far deeper into the day.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"At \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"Royal Drottningholm\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/success-stories/drottningholm\",\"uuid\":\"5c6091cb-c657-42db-a8dc-94bbfbe8971d\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]},{\"text\":\" in Sweden, the indoor studio has changed what winter looks like for members like Katarina Skärblom. Here, the Nordic winter has gone from off-season to very much switched on.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"“I spend more time at the golf club since we built the indoor studio with Trackman — especially during winter,”\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\"}]},{\"text\":\" says Katarina.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Read the full story of Royal Drottningholm Golf Club\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/success-stories/drottningholm\",\"uuid\":\"5c6091cb-c657-42db-a8dc-94bbfbe8971d\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"m\",\"_uid\":\"f580c311-3320-4e6d-970e-204e13957eb1\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"78598725-289d-4af1-8d2d-0dd0417daf4c\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"When golf clubs become community hubs\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"When a golf club becomes more engaging, it naturally becomes more social. Trackman has transformed facilities into lively spaces where families, casual players, committed golfers, and beginners spend more time practicing, playing, and socializing.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The energy spills into evenings, weekends, and community routines in a way traditional clubs can find difficult to achieve. At Eaglewood, Huish says the change is impossible to miss — because he sees it almost every night.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"be5ffc71-57b5-4bc0-abb1-cfe899d8a041\",\"image\":{\"id\":111318821909661,\"alt\":\"Elderly man with a white beard wearing a white USA cap and red polo shirt, outdoors with a blurred green background.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"profile_court\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/786x786/d26cffd11d/profile_court.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Elderly man with a white beard wearing a white USA cap and red polo shirt, outdoors with a blurred green background.\",\"title\":\"profile_court\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"quote\":\"The local community has responded in a remarkable way. I live two blocks from the golf course and you can’t believe the families and excitement going on at 7-8-9 o’clock at night now. There’s just a hub of action going on.\",\"author\":\"Court Huish\",\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"ui_quote\",\"dark_theme\":false,\"author_title\":\"Member at Eaglewood Golf Course\"},{\"_uid\":\"f45c474a-c666-4251-9688-c1961faf0197\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"hard_break\"},{\"text\":\"Bonding and competition: More reasons to show up\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Engagement doesn’t just give golfers more reasons to keep coming back, it helps grow club cultures. Weekly events, competitions, and league formats keep players connected with rituals that can run year-round.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"At Drottningholm, men’s and women’s events are held on a weekly basis, boosting the club’s social and competitive fabric.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"“A group of the ladies wanted to try some winter tournaments in the studio, and it was fun and something we wanted more of. You get to know the members, to compete, and get that feeling of being part of a club,”\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\"}]},{\"text\":\" said Katarina.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"At Black Desert, Mike describes that same dynamic playing out through simulator league play and shared moments with friends.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"“We did a simulator league this past spring and it did really well. Coming here and breaking up the week a little bit with a nice simulator round with your buddies is phenomenal,”\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\"}]},{\"text\":\" says Mike.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"9d67ef30-73f1-43d1-8121-8650edd2fe37\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"9747d79c-a953-4cc0-b5fc-f888cf14c47d\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Growing the next generation of junior golfers\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"One of the clearest signs of a healthy club is young golfers showing up — when kids can connect their swing to a visible result, practice becomes fun — and skill development accelerates. Trackman 360 helps juniors learn through feedback they can see immediately, and it gives coaches a more engaging way to teach fundamentals.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"At Eaglewood, member and committee chairman John Logan points to a noticeable increase in youth participation and junior talent programming because they’re learning in a more interactive, structured way.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"“It’s very pleasing to see the huge number of young people that are coming here, and there are more youth programs now because they can come up and learn and each one can see what he’s doing. The community has responded by just turning out in numbers,”\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\"}]},{\"text\":\" says John.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"984007d1-f587-4b96-8b23-4faeca379cde\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"6428f97f-295c-4908-bad8-59d38cf98af7\",\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"post_video\",\"video_url\":\"https://vimeo.com/1132110956/a827fe3b58?share=copy\u0026fl=sv\u0026fe=ci\",\"play_icon_theme\":\"white\",\"video_thumbnail\":{\"id\":152030413356334,\"alt\":\"Elderly man in a golf shirt and cap sits outdoors in a shaded area, with a golf course visible in the background.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"360_players_john_thumbnail\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/3840x2160/0c357a4476/360_players_john_thumbnail.jpg\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Elderly man in a golf shirt and cap sits outdoors in a shaded area, with a golf course visible in the background.\",\"title\":\"360_players_john_thumbnail\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false}},{\"_uid\":\"f8642128-7ed3-4bd4-8aff-0d851928db10\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Elevating the overall golf club experience\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Trackman’s impact isn’t limited to the ball flight screen. It changes the entire feel of the facility — from how modern it looks, to how premium it feels, to how long players want to stay. When practice becomes both informative and entertaining, the club becomes a place that players choose to spend time, not just briefly pass through.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"At Eaglewood, John describes how the technology has changed the way the facility is viewed — elevating the identity of the club itself.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"m\",\"_uid\":\"0c2f5622-3bfa-4581-a9f4-dd70e84489ab\",\"bottom\":\"none\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"8454e58b-a790-4916-a9b7-c842334222e9\",\"image\":{\"id\":111315223155505,\"alt\":\"Elderly man in a blue polo and cap, smiling. He wears a name tag and is outdoors with blurred greenery in the background.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"john_profile\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/400x400/04238e3df2/john_profile.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Elderly man in a blue polo and cap, smiling. He wears a name tag and is outdoors with blurred greenery in the background.\",\"title\":\"john_profile\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"quote\":\"Trackman 360 has really added class to our facility. It’s changed the view of the club to be much more of a practice facility and not so much just a strictly golf course.\",\"author\":\"John Logan\",\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"ui_quote\",\"dark_theme\":false,\"author_title\":\"Member and Community Chairman at Eaglewood Golf Course\"},{\"_uid\":\"938a1153-731e-431a-9083-faee88b05778\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"hard_break\"},{\"text\":\"From A to Tee: A connected player journey\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Across three very different clubs, players are describing the same shift: golf feels more connected. The experience begins upon arrival and stays cohesive across practice, play, coaching, and competition — indoors and outdoors.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Trackman 360 doesn’t replace what golfers love about their club — it strengthens it. By connecting practice, play, coaching, and competition, it turns isolated touchpoints into one cohesive experience. And when everything connects, golfers don’t just improve — they belong.\u2028\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"hard_break\"},{\"text\":\"Trackman 360: Powering Clubs. Empowering Players. \",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/lp/trackman-360\",\"uuid\":\"79bd296d-af16-4bd4-a9b2-6adf472b3da3\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"15efa298-7376-48b7-9f5c-cb900b1c68a7\",\"bottom\":\"xl\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false}],\"intro\":\"Growing the player-club connection\",\"theme\":\"light\",\"header\":[{\"_uid\":\"a9083a5a-6e93-4249-995e-4e4cec175a34\",\"theme\":[],\"title\":\"How Trackman 360 transforms the golf club for players\u2028\",\"component\":\"blog_post_header\"}],\"card_img\":{\"id\":154418725967435,\"alt\":\"Illustration of a person standing with a golf club and golf bag, surrounded by text: \\\"Range,\\\" \\\"Indoor,\\\" \\\"360.\\\" Simple line art style.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"trackman_360_players_blog_card\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/780x1040/bd765649fd/trackman_360_players_blog_card.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Illustration of a person standing with a golf club and golf bag, surrounded by text: \\\"Range,\\\" \\\"Indoor,\\\" \\\"360.\\\" Simple line art style.\",\"title\":\"trackman_360_players_blog_card\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"component\":\"blog_page\",\"card_video\":{\"id\":null,\"alt\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":null,\"title\":null,\"source\":null,\"filename\":\"\",\"copyright\":null,\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{}},\"carousel_img\":{\"id\":154418726045260,\"alt\":\"Minimalistic black banner with a stylized person holding a device. Text reads \\\"360\\\" surrounded by \\\"INDOOR,\\\" \\\"APP,\\\" \\\"BUSINESS,\\\" and \\\"RANGE.\\\"\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"trackman_360_players_blog_header\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/3840x1200/2cae11143b/trackman_360_players_blog_header.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Minimalistic black banner with a stylized person holding a device. Text reads \\\"360\\\" surrounded by \\\"INDOOR,\\\" \\\"APP,\\\" \\\"BUSINESS,\\\" and \\\"RANGE.\\\"\",\"title\":\"trackman_360_players_blog_header\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"card_video_url\":\"\",\"layout_variant\":\"blog\"},\"slug\":\"how-trackman-360-transforms-the-golf-club-for-players\",\"full_slug\":\"blog/golf/how-trackman-360-transforms-the-golf-club-for-players\",\"sort_by_date\":null,\"position\":-1110,\"tag_list\":[],\"is_startpage\":false,\"parent_id\":147199995,\"meta_data\":null,\"group_id\":\"31ac5d4f-6eb6-4898-be4b-078b3838713f\",\"first_published_at\":\"2026-03-13T08:23:12.422Z\",\"release_id\":null,\"lang\":\"default\",\"path\":null,\"alternates\":[],\"default_full_slug\":\"blog/golf/how-trackman-360-transforms-the-golf-club-for-players\",\"translated_slugs\":[{\"path\":\"blog/golf/how-trackman-360-transforms-the-golf-club-for-players\",\"name\":null,\"lang\":\"zh-cn\",\"published\":null},{\"path\":\"blog/golf/how-trackman-360-transforms-the-golf-club-for-players\",\"name\":null,\"lang\":\"ko\",\"published\":null},{\"path\":\"blog/golf/how-trackman-360-transforms-the-golf-club-for-players\",\"name\":null,\"lang\":\"it\",\"published\":null},{\"path\":\"blog/golf/how-trackman-360-transforms-the-golf-club-for-players\",\"name\":null,\"lang\":\"es\",\"published\":null},{\"path\":\"blog/golf/how-trackman-360-transforms-the-golf-club-for-players\",\"name\":null,\"lang\":\"fr\",\"published\":null},{\"path\":\"blog/golf/how-trackman-360-transforms-the-golf-club-for-players\",\"name\":null,\"lang\":\"de\",\"published\":null},{\"path\":\"blog/golf/how-trackman-360-transforms-the-golf-club-for-players\",\"name\":null,\"lang\":\"ja\",\"published\":null}]}}]}]}]}],[\"$\",\"$L14\",\"151966359981502\",{\"href\":\"/blog/golf/the-omega-european-masters-virtual-qualifier\",\"className\":\"w-full min-w-[320px] xl:max-w-[340px]\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$b1\",null,{\"fallback\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-full h-[130px] md:h-[480px] overflow-hidden grid border-none shadow-lg\"}],\"children\":[\"$\",\"$Lb2\",null,{\"reason\":\"next/dynamic\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$Lba\",null,{\"cardData\":{\"name\":\"From the simulator to the Swiss Alps\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T09:52:42.097Z\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:30:32.878Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:30:32.893Z\",\"id\":151966359981502,\"uuid\":\"59525247-8152-4b91-b522-b68b863c14a3\",\"content\":{\"seo\":{\"_uid\":\"a17e7e79-ed0d-49ba-9eff-b6a7516faf2d\",\"title\":\"From the simulator to the Swiss Alps\",\"plugin\":\"seo_metatags\",\"og_image\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/1200x630/a08c99bede/og_omega_blog.webp\",\"og_title\":\"From the simulator to the Swiss Alps\",\"description\":\"Compete on Trackman’s virtual Crans-sur-Sierre course and earn a wild card shot at the 2026 Omega European Masters on the DP World Tour.\",\"twitter_image\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/1200x630/a08c99bede/og_omega_blog.webp\",\"twitter_title\":\"From the simulator to the Swiss Alps\",\"og_description\":\"Compete on Trackman’s virtual Crans-sur-Sierre course and earn a wild card shot at the 2026 Omega European Masters on the DP World Tour.\",\"twitter_description\":\"Compete on Trackman’s virtual Crans-sur-Sierre course and earn a wild card shot at the 2026 Omega European Masters on the DP World Tour.\"},\"_uid\":\"cc19c70d-0bf1-48c5-be78-31e5c8b1219a\",\"body\":[{\"_uid\":\"722fd827-e4d3-4dff-9838-79a605db06c8\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Earn your wild card into the 2026 DP World Tour\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"bold\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"There is a moment in every elite player's development when they just need the right stage to prove their game. This is that stage.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Once again, the Omega European Masters is partnering with Trackman to deliver an immersive virtual golf experience with massive real-world stakes. Male professional and elite amateur players worldwide now have a direct pathway to compete for a wild card entry into the 2026 DP World Tour's Omega European Masters.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"b25d4886-f3d8-4978-aacc-c132d7ece80f\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"01a5887a-a344-4818-b2a5-4fb0cec02b3e\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The Qualifier: What you need to know\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"From March 1–31, players can step into any Trackman simulator and test their game on the meticulously rendered Virtual Golf 3 layout of Golf Club Crans-sur-Sierre.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"It all comes down to 18 holes of virtual stroke play. Here is how the pathway unfolds:\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"bullet_list\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"list_item\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The Virtual Qualifier (March 1–31):\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"bold\"}]},{\"text\":\" Post your best 18-hole score on the virtual Crans-sur-Sierre track.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list_item\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The Playoff (September 1):\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"bold\"}]},{\"text\":\" The top three players advance to a final 3-for-1 playoff on the actual Severiano Ballesteros Championship Course in Switzerland at 9:00 a.m. To help get you there, this is a travel cost-supported trip. Upon full completion of the physical qualifier, the top three players will receive 80% of the prize pool amount (split 35% for 1st, 30% for 2nd, and 25% for 3rd) to use toward travel expenses.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"list_item\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The Main Event (September 3–6):\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"bold\"}]},{\"text\":\" The playoff winner secures a coveted spot in the field for the 2026 Omega European Masters.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Think you have what it takes? \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"Enter here.\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"https://portal.trackmangolf.com/player/tournaments/TXVsdGlSb3VuZFRvdXJuYW1lbnQKZDlhMGUyODYzLTZkNDQtNGIwOC04NjJiLTYxNjU2NzU5ZWYxYjpQdWJsaXNoZWQ=/details?source=invite\",\"uuid\":null,\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"url\"}}]}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"a31d61f3-de80-41fd-933d-efecc5895a15\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"7c868777-d6ab-44ac-b496-b58666d327a8\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The blueprint: Jordan Weber’s mountain run\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"If you want to understand the realities of this crossover, look at last year’s champion.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"American Jordan Weber had been away from professional golf for more than a decade before using the NEXT Golf Tour to sharpen his competitive edge. During last year’s virtual qualifier, the top three spots were claimed by Anton Kiddy Nilsson, Blake Sattler, and Jordan Weber.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Weber ultimately prevailed in the on-site qualifier, booking his second-ever DP World Tour start.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The transition from the bay to the mountains? Seamless.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"\\\"\",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"The course played very similarly to how it plays on the simulator,\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\"}]},{\"text\":\"\\\" Weber said after wrapping up his second round in Switzerland. \\\"\",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"As far as how far the ball goes and what spots you hit it to, it really did prepare me in that way.\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\"}]},{\"text\":\"\\\"\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"f0da05a4-d84e-4d76-a327-73ec68858ae3\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"17cfb647-71de-4ff8-bb87-b8022cfaa5d5\",\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"post_video\",\"video_url\":\"https://vimeo.com/1170979975/ab934cd042?share=copy\u0026fl=sv\u0026fe=ci\",\"play_icon_theme\":\"white\",\"video_thumbnail\":{\"id\":151982471417769,\"alt\":\"Golfer in blue swings club at tee; spectators stand nearby. Omega logo on large red display in background.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"omega_thumbnail\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/1672x946/05431a2100/omega_thumbnail.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Golfer in blue swings club at tee; spectators stand nearby. Omega logo on large red display in background.\",\"title\":\"omega_thumbnail\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false}},{\"_uid\":\"2bbceab4-a5ed-4ca7-9815-21065ff3968d\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"More than a tournament\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The experience went far beyond the fairways. Weber found himself hitting balls next to the world's best, watching major champions like Matt Fitzpatrick dial in yardages during a fog delay.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Later, on the range, he struck up a conversation with DP World Tour winner Matt Wallace. When Weber asked for a photo, Wallace immediately recognized him from his simulator triumphs.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"\\\"\",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"Whoa, you know who I am?\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\"}]},{\"text\":\"\\\" Weber recalled with a laugh. \\\"\",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"That was so cool. Thank you, Matt, for making my day.\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\"}]},{\"text\":\"\\\"\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"m\",\"_uid\":\"e6203921-c752-430e-87d8-1c9f00602d7c\",\"bottom\":\"none\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"e92e4f55-3215-4531-83d9-22290b14c8bc\",\"image\":{\"id\":151984383365375,\"alt\":\"Two men smiling on a golf course, one in a grey polo and cap, the other in a navy outfit and cap, with golf clubs and trees in the background.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"weber_omega_image\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/550x550/ed01d34cde/weber_omega_image.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Two men smiling on a golf course, one in a grey polo and cap, the other in a navy outfit and cap, with golf clubs and trees in the background.\",\"title\":\"weber_omega_image\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"post_image\",\"dark_theme\":false,\"description\":\"Jordan Weber and Matt Wallace\",\"mobile_image\":{\"id\":151984383365375,\"alt\":\"Two men smiling on a golf course, one in a grey polo and cap, the other in a navy outfit and cap, with golf clubs and trees in the background.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"weber_omega_image\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/550x550/ed01d34cde/weber_omega_image.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Two men smiling on a golf course, one in a grey polo and cap, the other in a navy outfit and cap, with golf clubs and trees in the background.\",\"title\":\"weber_omega_image\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"actual_size_image\":true},{\"_uid\":\"36c3675e-5e9c-4e47-8858-08459c2038c2\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Trackman and the NEXT Golf Tour continue to make golfing dreams come true, proving that great golf doesn't just happen on tour; it starts in the simulator.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Fire up a session, dial in your numbers, and post your score. The Swiss Alps are waiting.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"hard_break\"},{\"text\":\"Read more\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"https://www.omegaeuropeanmasters.com/tournament/virtual\",\"uuid\":null,\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"url\"}}]}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"m\",\"_uid\":\"9f254f4f-8e91-4947-abbe-0f6022500ea3\",\"bottom\":\"xl\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false}],\"intro\":\"The Omega European Masters virtual qualifier returns\",\"theme\":\"light\",\"header\":[{\"_uid\":\"a9083a5a-6e93-4249-995e-4e4cec175a34\",\"theme\":[],\"title\":\"From the simulator to the Swiss Alps\",\"component\":\"blog_post_header\"}],\"card_img\":{\"id\":151970328868074,\"alt\":\"Omega Masters 2026 logo on blurred mountain background, with event details: Crans Montana, Golf Club Crans-Sur-Sierre, 3-6.09.2026.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"omega_blog_card\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/780x1040/bc7ec090ae/omega_blog_card.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Omega Masters 2026 logo on blurred mountain background, with event details: Crans Montana, Golf Club Crans-Sur-Sierre, 3-6.09.2026.\",\"title\":\"omega_blog_card\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"component\":\"blog_page\",\"card_video\":{\"id\":null,\"alt\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":null,\"title\":null,\"source\":null,\"filename\":\"\",\"copyright\":null,\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{}},\"carousel_img\":{\"id\":151990315995729,\"alt\":\"A golfer bends over on a scenic course with mountains in the background; Omega Masters 2026 event logo is on the right.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"omega_blog_header.webp\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/3840x1200/bb0d28b59f/omega_blog_header.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"A golfer bends over on a scenic course with mountains in the background; Omega Masters 2026 event logo is on the right.\",\"title\":\"omega_blog_header.webp\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"card_video_url\":\"\",\"layout_variant\":\"blog\"},\"slug\":\"the-omega-european-masters-virtual-qualifier\",\"full_slug\":\"blog/golf/the-omega-european-masters-virtual-qualifier\",\"sort_by_date\":null,\"position\":-1100,\"tag_list\":[],\"is_startpage\":false,\"parent_id\":147199995,\"meta_data\":null,\"group_id\":\"dd6bdff4-589b-4c2d-bf7c-cc3502b65724\",\"first_published_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:18:32.391Z\",\"release_id\":null,\"lang\":\"default\",\"path\":null,\"alternates\":[],\"default_full_slug\":\"blog/golf/the-omega-european-masters-virtual-qualifier\",\"translated_slugs\":[{\"path\":\"blog/golf/the-omega-european-masters-virtual-qualifier\",\"name\":null,\"lang\":\"zh-cn\",\"published\":null},{\"path\":\"blog/golf/the-omega-european-masters-virtual-qualifier\",\"name\":null,\"lang\":\"ko\",\"published\":null},{\"path\":\"blog/golf/the-omega-european-masters-virtual-qualifier\",\"name\":null,\"lang\":\"it\",\"published\":null},{\"path\":\"blog/golf/the-omega-european-masters-virtual-qualifier\",\"name\":null,\"lang\":\"es\",\"published\":null},{\"path\":\"blog/golf/the-omega-european-masters-virtual-qualifier\",\"name\":null,\"lang\":\"fr\",\"published\":null},{\"path\":\"blog/golf/the-omega-european-masters-virtual-qualifier\",\"name\":null,\"lang\":\"de\",\"published\":null},{\"path\":\"blog/golf/the-omega-european-masters-virtual-qualifier\",\"name\":null,\"lang\":\"ja\",\"published\":null}]}}]}]}]}],[\"$\",\"$L14\",\"149479414001327\",{\"href\":\"/blog/golf/garage-golf-simulator\",\"className\":\"w-full min-w-[320px] xl:max-w-[340px]\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$b1\",null,{\"fallback\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-full h-[130px] md:h-[480px] overflow-hidden grid border-none shadow-lg\"}],\"children\":[\"$\",\"$Lb2\",null,{\"reason\":\"next/dynamic\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$Lba\",null,{\"cardData\":{\"name\":\"Garage Golf Simulator: The ultimate setup with Trackman\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-27T09:13:17.549Z\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-03T09:54:19.296Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T09:54:19.328Z\",\"id\":149479414001327,\"uuid\":\"a377c401-37ba-4da8-a46c-05fac9fc4c7c\",\"content\":{\"seo\":{\"_uid\":\"a17e7e79-ed0d-49ba-9eff-b6a7516faf2d\",\"title\":\"Garage Golf Simulator: The Ultimate Setup with Trackman\",\"plugin\":\"seo_metatags\",\"og_image\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/1200x630/09f06236e4/og_garage_golf_simulator_blog.webp\",\"og_title\":\"Garage Golf Simulator: The Ultimate Setup with Trackman\",\"description\":\"Build the ultimate garage golf simulator with Trackman 4 or Trackman iO. Enjoy ultra-realistic 4K golf at home. Setup tips plus DIY or custom build options.\",\"twitter_image\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/1200x630/09f06236e4/og_garage_golf_simulator_blog.webp\",\"twitter_title\":\"Garage Golf Simulator: The Ultimate Setup with Trackman\",\"og_description\":\"Build the ultimate garage golf simulator with Trackman 4 or Trackman iO. Enjoy ultra-realistic 4K golf at home. Setup tips plus DIY or custom build options.\",\"twitter_description\":\"Build the ultimate garage golf simulator with Trackman 4 or Trackman iO. Enjoy ultra-realistic 4K golf at home. Setup tips plus DIY or custom build options.\"},\"_uid\":\"cc19c70d-0bf1-48c5-be78-31e5c8b1219a\",\"body\":[{\"_uid\":\"f67bf2a2-cab6-4282-8167-008293fce209\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Imagine if you had a garage golf simulator and you could play golf at any time in any weather. Now imagine the gameplay was ultra-realistic, like playing in real life. Who wouldn’t want to practice by playing a top tier course in 4K rather than taking a rainy day on the range? \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Enter Trackman, the golf shot tracking technology that revolutionized the sport. \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The Trackman iO enables you to \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"build a golf simulator\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/golf/simulator/\",\"uuid\":\"e45050b1-5c4f-4d92-81f6-538938874991\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]},{\"text\":\" right into your home. If a golf simulator is on your radar, today’s read will be just for you. We’ll take a closer look at how you can get the ultimate indoor golf experience customized to your exact wants and needs. Let’s roll! \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null}}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"53ca7606-793b-429b-8101-6f61788fe898\",\"bottom\":\"\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"9d3bfe8b-d8de-4e0c-a30f-abcc7dab1f8f\",\"image\":{\"id\":150904760385034,\"alt\":\"Indoor golf simulator setup in a modern room with a large screen displaying a golf course, golf clubs on a stand, and a parked car.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_garage.webp\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/1672x942/459030c006/garage_golf_simulator_blog_garage.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Indoor golf simulator setup in a modern room with a large screen displaying a golf course, golf clubs on a stand, and a parked car.\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_garage.webp\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"post_image\",\"dark_theme\":false,\"description\":\"\",\"mobile_image\":{\"id\":150904760385034,\"alt\":\"Indoor golf simulator setup in a modern room with a large screen displaying a golf course, golf clubs on a stand, and a parked car.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_garage.webp\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/1672x942/459030c006/garage_golf_simulator_blog_garage.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Indoor golf simulator setup in a modern room with a large screen displaying a golf course, golf clubs on a stand, and a parked car.\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_garage.webp\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"actual_size_image\":true},{\"_uid\":\"5f5dec30-4a70-4333-abab-138447f1f5d1\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"hard_break\"},{\"text\":\"What’s a golf simulator?\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"A golf simulator is a technology that simulates a real world golf experience by combining hardware, software, and a physical space to swing the golf club. The hardware, the engine of the simulator, is the \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"Trackman 4\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/golf/launch-monitors/trackman-4\",\"uuid\":\"fc388458-1b3c-48e0-80d5-dc64aadbfbd2\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]},{\"text\":\" or the \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"Trackman iO\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/golf/launch-monitors/trackman-io\",\"uuid\":\"c2cd463f-d3ce-46aa-839d-0c1eb58c2977\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]},{\"text\":\" launch monitor that uses radar technology to track the golf shot and simulate it virtually. \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Before the golf launch monitor was invented by Trackman just over 20 years ago, golfers and instructors guesstimated the data of a golf shot from the golfer’s swing and the flight of the ball. Trackman revolutionized the game by enabling players and instructors to get accurate data to improve their game. Today, Trackman 4 is the industry-leading launch monitor and golf simulator. \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":3,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"hard_break\"},{\"text\":\"How Trackman golf simulators work\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The iconic orange box leverages radar and camera technology to accurately measure club and ball data such as attack angle, club speed, spin rate, and much more. Trackman 4 gives players insights into more than 40 parameters of a golf shot. \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null}},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null}}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"2a668c15-65d7-4893-8d1b-6f9d70d98dcf\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"a467ba17-3e5f-4cfa-86ff-bc2f3a81a680\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Choosing between a portable and a garage golf simulator\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"When picking the right Trackman golf simulator setup for your game, it’s crucial to know what you’re looking for. The main thing to decide is whether you need an indoor golf simulator for your garage, or if you need a portable launch monitor that can be used both indoors at home and outdoors on the range. \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"If you’re looking for a portable launch monitor to bring to the range and use for indoor golf at home, the Trackman 4 is the best solution on the market. Trackman 4 uses optically enhanced radar tracking (OERT) sensors, one for short range and one for long range, to be able to deliver the most precise data of your golf shots. Trackman 4 starts at USD 25,495.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"cta\":[{\"url\":{\"id\":\"bf020364-a37a-49c9-a0f9-40bb985d28ca\",\"url\":\"\",\"linktype\":\"story\",\"fieldtype\":\"multilink\",\"cached_url\":\"golf/launch-monitors/get-your-own\"},\"_uid\":\"0872208d-6ab2-4c10-afaa-9cb6666d6ec6\",\"label\":\"Get your own\",\"component\":\"link\",\"variation\":\"primary\"}],\"_uid\":\"c57a4866-a23a-4d79-a9e1-195979e40a7a\",\"image\":{\"id\":null,\"alt\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":null,\"title\":null,\"source\":null,\"filename\":\"\",\"copyright\":null,\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{}},\"video\":{\"id\":null,\"alt\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":null,\"title\":null,\"source\":null,\"filename\":\"\",\"copyright\":null,\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{}},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"ac6e23e5-fb63-4d74-95c4-e168e3b2e405\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"media_with_text\",\"video_url\":\"\",\"dark_theme\":false,\"image_fill\":\"cover\",\"rich_content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\"}]},\"layout_mobile\":\"img_top\",\"layout_desktop\":\"img_right\",\"video_thumbnail\":{\"id\":null,\"alt\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":null,\"title\":null,\"source\":null,\"filename\":\"\",\"copyright\":null,\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{}},\"image_aspect_ratio\":\"1/1\"},{\"_uid\":\"16c27c5a-c576-4efa-b80b-f87738b19b09\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Golf simulator for garage setups\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"One of the main rooms that customers build a golf simulator into is the garage. It’s often ideal as it’s easy to clear out to make room, it’s private so you can focus on your game, and it’s separate from the house so your smashed drives won’t disturb your family. Other popular choices for putting the simulator is the basement, spare rooms, or a garden shed that can be converted into your personal golf training facility. \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Discover how Chris Djuric, a UK-based man with a passion for golf, found a way to balance family and golf by installing a customized Trackman iO simulator in his garage and transforming his UK home into a year-round golf haven.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"From Garage to Home Golf Simulator\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/success-stories/chris-djuric\",\"uuid\":\"4f58a027-f708-4aac-ba1c-e1587d8f7fa9\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"fb65c6ce-bd2f-4053-b84c-92ed86ca74c1\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"f7523704-7149-4ef5-b724-151e1aa3fe73\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The ultimate golf simulator setup for your home\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Trackman 4 is the gold standard in golf. It is adopted by thousands of coaches and clubs, and is the go-to solution by 90 out of the top 100 players in the world. However, the \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"Trackman iO \",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/golf/launch-monitors/trackman-io\",\"uuid\":\"c2cd463f-d3ce-46aa-839d-0c1eb58c2977\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]},{\"text\":\"may be a more optimal solution if you already have access to Trackman Range in your club and are looking for the best indoor golf simulator available for your home. \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Like Trackman 4, the Trackman iO uses radar and high speed camera technology to pull club and ball data from a golf shot. It differs from the portable Trackman 4 by being a built-in solution for your home. With the iO, you can immerse yourself in Trackman Virtual Golf 3, the most realistic gameplay that enables you to play top courses in 4K - right there in your garage, basement or elsewhere in your home. \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Trackman iO is available as a \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"complete home solution\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/golf/simulator/build-outs\",\"uuid\":\"4058e732-1ca0-4466-8c4b-133aa0921ec6\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]},{\"text\":\" with two different configurations; the Custom Integrated Build and the Standalone Flex Cage. \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Get inspired by our many satisfied customers. \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"Read their success stories here.\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/golf/simulator/success-stories\",\"uuid\":\"673e008d-6cfc-400b-b3ec-a96b165fc337\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":3,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"hard_break\"},{\"text\":\"Trackman iO Custom Integrated Build\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"a29d6e8a-3709-4a42-b3a3-016fc87602e2\",\"image\":{\"id\":149521439352985,\"alt\":\"Home golf simulator setup with a large screen displaying a lush golf course, surrounded by a modern living room with beige furniture and decor.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_custom\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/1672x942/4cc80cf686/garage_golf_simulator_blog_custom.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Home golf simulator setup with a large screen displaying a lush golf course, surrounded by a modern living room with beige furniture and decor.\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_custom\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"post_image\",\"dark_theme\":false,\"description\":\"\",\"mobile_image\":{\"id\":149521439352985,\"alt\":\"Home golf simulator setup with a large screen displaying a lush golf course, surrounded by a modern living room with beige furniture and decor.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_custom\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/1672x942/4cc80cf686/garage_golf_simulator_blog_custom.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Home golf simulator setup with a large screen displaying a lush golf course, surrounded by a modern living room with beige furniture and decor.\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_custom\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"actual_size_image\":true},{\"_uid\":\"5feaa7e4-9df3-4af1-a01a-c023f9ec2941\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The Trackman iO Custom Integrated Build is the ultimate golf simulator setup for your garage, basement, or a dedicated room. Starting at USD 47,990 including installation, the Custom Integrated Build is a tailored solution that is seamlessly built into your room of choice. This build-out is for golfers who want to permanently dedicate space for their simulator to get the most complete indoor golf experience available in the world. \",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"cta\":[{\"url\":{\"id\":\"e74ee51d-6d84-4843-950d-2a55e61cb61d\",\"url\":\"\",\"linktype\":\"story\",\"fieldtype\":\"multilink\",\"cached_url\":\"golf/simulator/get-your-own\"},\"_uid\":\"0b01f0ab-8164-42ec-9020-fe61ac66a443\",\"label\":\"Get your own\",\"component\":\"link\",\"variation\":\"primary\"}],\"_uid\":\"9ac77ed5-16ab-4045-95dc-d4c4c6b8b7fa\",\"image\":{\"id\":null,\"alt\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":null,\"title\":null,\"source\":null,\"filename\":\"\",\"copyright\":null,\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{}},\"video\":{\"id\":null,\"alt\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":null,\"title\":null,\"source\":null,\"filename\":\"\",\"copyright\":null,\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{}},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"e5a9bb9f-3ce9-48c5-8d5e-214c849a4044\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"media_with_text\",\"video_url\":\"\",\"dark_theme\":false,\"image_fill\":\"cover\",\"rich_content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\"}]},\"layout_mobile\":\"img_top\",\"layout_desktop\":\"img_right\",\"video_thumbnail\":{\"id\":null,\"alt\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":null,\"title\":null,\"source\":null,\"filename\":\"\",\"copyright\":null,\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{}},\"image_aspect_ratio\":\"1/1\"},{\"_uid\":\"21552537-d6df-4110-9c9e-e32d77f71fc9\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":3,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Trackman iO Standalone Flex Cage\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null}}]},\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"7211dc44-9de8-4fb5-ac67-2ba58f46f425\",\"image\":{\"id\":149527302498810,\"alt\":\"Indoor golf simulator setup with a large screen displaying practice options and lush green turf, set in a modern room with concrete walls.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_flex_cage.webp\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/1672x942/306f9ba2b2/garage_golf_simulator_blog_flex_cage.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Indoor golf simulator setup with a large screen displaying practice options and lush green turf, set in a modern room with concrete walls.\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_flex_cage.webp\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"post_image\",\"dark_theme\":false,\"description\":\"\",\"mobile_image\":{\"id\":149527302498810,\"alt\":\"Indoor golf simulator setup with a large screen displaying practice options and lush green turf, set in a modern room with concrete walls.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_flex_cage.webp\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/1672x942/306f9ba2b2/garage_golf_simulator_blog_flex_cage.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Indoor golf simulator setup with a large screen displaying practice options and lush green turf, set in a modern room with concrete walls.\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_flex_cage.webp\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"actual_size_image\":true},{\"_uid\":\"b3bcb578-4a27-4dd1-8774-b20b885f0064\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The Trackman iO Standalone Flex Cage is an easy to install solution that can be used as a short or long-term golf simulator. The Flex Cage is modular and movable so you can change your mind later and move it to another area. It’s great for players who want to get started with their golf simulator as quickly as possible without having to plan where to permanently build in the tech. The Standalone Flex Cage including installation starts at USD 43,995.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Head over to our \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"Sim Builder\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/golf/simulator/sim-builder\",\"uuid\":\"1b2a28cc-e0d2-445a-8462-a60e2a75df3d\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]},{\"text\":\" to start designing your dream golf simulator setup.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},\"padding\":[],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"cta\":[{\"url\":{\"id\":\"e74ee51d-6d84-4843-950d-2a55e61cb61d\",\"url\":\"\",\"linktype\":\"story\",\"fieldtype\":\"multilink\",\"cached_url\":\"golf/simulator/get-your-own\"},\"_uid\":\"20728aba-8ed7-4bed-b80d-fabdf80bbded\",\"label\":\"Get your own\",\"component\":\"link\",\"variation\":\"primary\"}],\"_uid\":\"a3c83acf-8f02-40c1-9501-b47f7dde8423\",\"image\":{\"id\":null,\"alt\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":null,\"title\":null,\"source\":null,\"filename\":\"\",\"copyright\":null,\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{}},\"video\":{\"id\":null,\"alt\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":null,\"title\":null,\"source\":null,\"filename\":\"\",\"copyright\":null,\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{}},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"c9eb15c5-1868-46f7-a16d-eb288612328d\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"media_with_text\",\"video_url\":\"\",\"dark_theme\":false,\"image_fill\":\"cover\",\"rich_content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\"}]},\"layout_mobile\":\"img_top\",\"layout_desktop\":\"img_right\",\"video_thumbnail\":{\"id\":null,\"alt\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":null,\"title\":null,\"source\":null,\"filename\":\"\",\"copyright\":null,\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{}},\"image_aspect_ratio\":\"1/1\"},{\"_uid\":\"389879a4-66c2-4560-b613-f6cf09a896fa\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"How to build a golf simulator yourself\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"At Trackman, we’ve spent 20 years of engineering perfecting our military-grade radar technology. Put in another way, it would be difficult for you to develop the technology for a homemade golf simulator. However, it’s definitely doable to build the setup around the tech. \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"That’s why we offer the Trackman iO Tech Setup in addition to the Integrated Build and the Flex Cage. \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":3,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"hard_break\"},{\"text\":\"Trackman iO Tech Setup\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"The Trackman iO Tech Setup is for the handy golfer who’s looking for a DIY golf simulator solution. Starting at USD 20,000, the Tech Setup pack includes the Trackman iO launch monitor, computer and projector. With all the essentials included, the Tech Setup allows you to design your very own DIY golf simulator setup around the Trackman iO device. \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Using our Sim Builder\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/golf/simulator/sim-builder\",\"uuid\":\"1b2a28cc-e0d2-445a-8462-a60e2a75df3d\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]},{\"text\":\", simply choose Tech Setup as your build-out option to get started.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"If you’re looking for inspiration on how this could look, check out some of \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"our previous builds.\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/golf/simulator/build-outs\",\"uuid\":\"4058e732-1ca0-4466-8c4b-133aa0921ec6\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]}]}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"ce84cb78-3089-44a4-9037-30ffd2c8127c\",\"bottom\":\"m\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false},{\"_uid\":\"ac1d938b-a7b5-4d44-bb56-f9cf252bf0b2\",\"content\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Choosing the right place for your golf simulator\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"When figuring out which area to dedicate to golf, the most important thing is that you’ll need space to swing your club. If you decide to go with the Trackman iO, you’d need a ceiling height of around 10 feet, 10 ft room depth, and 15 feet width for comfortable swing space. \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Unlike the Trackman iO which is mounted to the ceiling, if you’re choosing the Trackman 4 Launch Monitor for your home golf simulator, you’d need more room depth for the launch monitor to be able to properly track your shots. Oh, and remember to limit the amount of windows in your golf simulator space - balls will be flying! \",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"Before ordering, make sure the room is ideal for your setup. We’re happy to help - \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"talk to a Trackman expert\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/golf/simulator/get-your-own\",\"uuid\":\"e74ee51d-6d84-4843-950d-2a55e61cb61d\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]},{\"text\":\" today to get guidance!\",\"type\":\"text\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"hard_break\"},{\"text\":\"Read more: \",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"How much room do you need for a golf simulator?\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"/blog/golf/how-much-room-for-a-golf-simulator\",\"uuid\":\"703a2b1c-8d85-43dc-883c-a767e4258d33\",\"anchor\":null,\"target\":\"_self\",\"linktype\":\"story\"}}]}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null}}]},\"padding\":[{\"top\":\"none\",\"_uid\":\"acc7c6ad-73c2-4584-a51a-c4bc0e801cb0\",\"bottom\":\"xl\",\"component\":\"padding\"}],\"component\":\"rich_text\",\"dark_theme\":false}],\"intro\":\"Tired of rainy days on the range?\",\"theme\":\"light\",\"header\":[{\"_uid\":\"a9083a5a-6e93-4249-995e-4e4cec175a34\",\"theme\":[],\"title\":\"Garage Golf Simulator: How to build the ultimate setup for your home with Trackman\",\"component\":\"blog_post_header\"}],\"card_img\":{\"id\":149521439348887,\"alt\":\"Indoor golf simulator in a modern garage with a golf bag, a car, and a large screen displaying a golf course under bright lighting.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_card\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/780x1040/2ff327c911/garage_golf_simulator_blog_card.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Indoor golf simulator in a modern garage with a golf bag, a car, and a large screen displaying a golf course under bright lighting.\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_card\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"component\":\"blog_page\",\"card_video\":{\"id\":null,\"alt\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":null,\"title\":null,\"source\":null,\"filename\":\"\",\"copyright\":null,\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{}},\"carousel_img\":{\"id\":149521439357082,\"alt\":\"Indoor golf simulator setup in a garage with a screen showing a golf course, a bag of clubs, and a parked car nearby.\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_header\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a.storyblok.com/f/117513/3840x1200/5a2181fa07/garage_golf_simulator_blog_header.webp\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{\"alt\":\"Indoor golf simulator setup in a garage with a screen showing a golf course, a bag of clubs, and a parked car nearby.\",\"title\":\"garage_golf_simulator_blog_header\",\"source\":\"\",\"copyright\":\"Trackman\"},\"is_external_url\":false},\"card_video_url\":\"\",\"layout_variant\":\"blog\"},\"slug\":\"garage-golf-simulator\",\"full_slug\":\"blog/golf/garage-golf-simulator\",\"sort_by_date\":null,\"position\":-1090,\"tag_list\":[],\"is_startpage\":false,\"parent_id\":147199995,\"meta_data\":null,\"group_id\":\"1f694472-0fda-4051-a7be-46172ba75007\",\"first_published_at\":\"2026-02-27T12:42:15.106Z\",\"release_id\":null,\"lang\":\"default\",\"path\":null,\"alternates\":[],\"default_full_slug\":\"blog/golf/garage-golf-simulator\",\"translated_slugs\":[{\"path\":\"blog/golf/garage-golf-simulator\",\"name\":null,\"lang\":\"zh-cn\",\"published\":null},{\"p